{"tid":1776054,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(突發) 大量連登仔中左五毛既圈套 ! 咁容易被分化香港同台灣友誼之交 !!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-12-09T09:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T14:35:07.000Z","uid":222970,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6b33a9c589dcca7d1b2bd53b87b44bd62ef102","tid":1776054,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"澳洲媒體引述王立強指，一個名為龔青（中國創新投資董事會主席兼行政總裁向心之妻）的女子直接負責在台灣操縱台灣選舉的工作。早在2018年，<span style=\"color: red;\">他已在三地建立了<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">20多萬個網絡帳號</span>來攻擊民進黨，又成立許多粉絲團來進行網絡霸凌。</span>另外，中時旺旺亦是其主要盟友。[6]<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有扮台仔屌柒香港人只係中共五毛，王立強已FC 至少有20萬隻五毛係各論壇帶風向！<br />\n<br />\n大家可以無視一切台灣五毛！！！依d只係中共玩分化手段！<br />\n<br />\n如果你因為網上言論而仇恨台灣人，咁就證明左你中左中共既分化陰謀<br />\n<br />\n唔明你地班人點解咁容易中計！！！？？？香港人同台灣人永遠係盟友！<br />\n<br />\n我正式宣佈邊個再分化香港同台灣就係五毛</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有片 ！ 揭發五毛軍團工場！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DeepStateExpose/status/1185671679885926400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDeepStateExpose%2Fstatus%2F1185671679885926400&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=bc93e4bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDeepStateExpose%2Fstatus%2F1185671679885926400&h=768b5446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DeepStateExpose/status/1185671679885926400</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4RvqD3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4RvqD3D.png&h=2a6ecbae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxQFsWZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxQFsWZ.png&h=ba2876fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e69d3a90b7657e9069d9dc80ee3f5f711593bb59","tid":1776054,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkg