係覺得你幼稚但係大方向唔會變.  就好似河童 &quot;請求&quot; 就解做 &quot;要求&quot;, 之後無限上綱到干涉人地選舉同自大.  咁你舉牌講 Trump 係咪同一樣道理? <br />\n<br />\n台灣大撚把工讀生收錢做野, 成個國家都滲透晒.  你係台灣網見到屌柒你香港根本未必係台灣人點諗.  人地氣候暖化個靚妹上聯合國講 How dare you.  你估氣候暖化 D 人有無講佢唔撚識野, 無讀過 IR? 識唔識禮儀?<br />\n<br />\n香港一直就係 D 老屎忽同以為自己好撚識野既高分低能把持.  有左 facebook 之後更加係火力全開不停傳教. 好撚心就自己屙督尿照下自己啦.  你就網上打飛機以為自己好撚勁好撚識野, 人地已經面向國際啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識慚愧都識睇形勢啦檬撚."},{"pid":"9a47d889842df93da2e9b7322127fa4d3fdb6d79","tid":1776054,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62675401cda442775c968fa3254a1f4ab7d3f673","tid":1776054,"uid":232949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n一朝起身見到啲post心諗做乜鳩<br />\n完全係小事化大"},{"pid":"7d9092340cc03d45085e0de694c4b4bc1f0a527b","tid":1776054,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22468e54e778e6ff73ca8d29e545e867e0b5cce4","tid":1776054,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f692a86b221f96aa01dfae9f2ceae71886dba368","tid":1776054,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04d834786b8e153fcb3b2cafdf61b79ece05702","tid":1776054,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}